title: Best of The Program | Guests: Kirstie Alley & Jason Buttrill | 11/3/20
description:
It’s Election Day 2020, and this generation has a chance to vote FOR something: Whether the American experiment should continue. Jason Buttrill breaks down the leftist protests already planned for tonight. Actress Kirstie Alley talks voting for Trump twice and feuding with CNN over its depressing coronavirus coverage.
